HEADWORD: Indehiscent
<hw>In`de*his"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>dehiscent</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>ind⟦eacute⟧hiscent</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Remaining
